<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>로그인 - RANKING AI</title>
    <style>
        body { background: #0b0c0d; color: #fff; font-family: 'Pretendard', sans-serif; display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; min-height: 100vh; margin: 0; padding: 20px; box-sizing: border-box; }
        .auth-container { background: #161718; padding: 40px; border-radius: 15px; border: 1px solid #222; width: 100%; max-width: 400px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box; }
        .logo { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 900; color: #00e5ff; margin-bottom: 30px; }
        input { width: 100%; background: #222; border: 1px solid #333; color: #fff; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 15px; box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; transition: 0.2s; }
        input:focus { border-color: #00e5ff; }
        .btn-submit { width: 100%; background: #00e5ff; color: #000; font-weight: bold; border: none; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; cursor: pointer; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 10px; transition: 0.2s; }
        .btn-submit:hover { filter: brightness(1.1); }
        .links { margin-top: 20px; font-size: 14px; color: #888; }
        .links a { color: #00e5ff; text-decoration: none; margin-left: 10px; }
        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .auth-container { padding: 30px 20px; }
            .logo { font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="auth-container">
        <div class="logo">RANKING AI</div>
        <form action="/login" method="POST">
            <input type="text" name="id" placeholder="아이디" required>
            <input type="password" name="pw" placeholder="비밀번호" required>
            <button type="submit" class="btn-submit">로그인</button>
        </form>
        <div class="links">
            아직 계정이 없으신가요? <a href="/signup">회원가입</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
